      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ali Bin Asbaat, from the one who reported it, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘There is no problem if there happen to be twenty shirts for the man’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "16. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ali ibn Asbat from the one who narrated to him who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘It is not unlawful if one has twenty shirts. 5 ” "
        ]
      }
